    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Quia quicquid pro amore Dei agitur hoc
                        procul dubio resurrecturis animabus profuturum non dubitamus, idcirco notum
                        sit omnibus fidelibus sancte Dei Ecclesie nostrisque presentibus et futuris,
                        nos in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/126"><rs
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >corte nostra </rs></geogName>in <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/59"><rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs> Veronensis</placeName>
                        iuxta <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4646"><rs key="#Rivers"
                                >flumen</rs> Athesim</placeName>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Penalty #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/516"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                            construxisse, quam in honorem Domini Salvatori eiusque
                            Genitricis</orgName> dedicare cupientes, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >res quasdam regni nostri</rs> pertinentes <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/124"><rs key="#Comitatus">de comitatu
                            Veronense</rs></geogName>, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >massaritiam</rs> unam in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs> Fontens,
                            <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Vici">vico</rs> scilicet Variano</placeName>, que regitur
                        per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #Royal_freedman"><name ref="Dago"
                                >Dagonem</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers #Royal_freedman">liberum hominem</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Wine">terram cum vineis</rs> in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Wine"
                            >Aquatraversa</placeName>, et massariciam unam <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1804">in vico Porciles</placeName>, insuper et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> que pertinet <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2051">de comitatu Vicentino</geogName>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1804">in eodem loco Porciles</placeName> et regitur per
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #Royal_freedman"><name
                                ref="Stabilis">Stabilem</name> liberum hominem</persName>, eidem et
                        devenire pro dotes scilicet secundum canonicam institutionem conferentes
                        statuimus et firmiter habendum eandem censemus ecclesiam, ut nullo umquam in
                        tempore aut regalis potestas easdem res a predicta ecclesia valeat
                        subtrahere ecclesia, sed in perpetuum stabilitate eas possideat et vindicet,
                        eo videlicet ordine, ut presbiter qui pro tempore in eadem eccleasia fuerit
                        ordinatus ac ad militandum constitutus ipsas res usufructuario nomine ad
                        victitandum habeat et teneat coad vixerit, et in nativitate domini nostri
                        Iesu Christi in ecclesiam eiudem genitricis Beate semper virginis Marie in
                        episcopio duos cereos pro censu presbyter annualiter offerat. Si quis
                        igitur, quod non credimus, contra hoc nostre institutionis seu concessionis
                        preceptum contra ire temptaverit, <rs key="#Penalty">auri obrici libras
                            centum</rs> solvere cogatur, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere
                            nostre</rs> et medietatem prelibate ecclesie ibique Deo militantibus.
                        Quod ut verius ab omnibus credatur, manu propria subter roborantes de anulo
                        nostro insigniri iussimus. Signum domni Berengarii serenissimi regis.
                            <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Dat. pridie kalendas
                        aprilis, anno dominice incarnationis . DCCCCXV., regni vero domni Berengarii
                        serenissimi regis .XXVIII., indictione .III. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/59">Verone</placeName>. in Dei nomine feliciter, amen. </ab>
